  Generating function over ALL 2^C(n,2) tournaments
======================================================================

--- n = 3 ---
  K_3(A) = 6*A^1 + 2*A^3
  Mean H = 1.5000
  n!/2^(n-1) = 1.5000
  Var H = 0.7500
  Mean H = n!/2^(n-1)? True
  K'_n(1)/K_n(1) = mean log_H = 0.2747
  Count ratios:
    K[H=3]/K[H=1] = 0.3333

